<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Loan Agreement</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 40px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .section h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .loan-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .loan-details table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .loan-details td {
            padding: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .loan-details td:first-child {
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 30%;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 60px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .signature-box {
            width: 45%;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            padding-top: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>LOAN AGREEMENT</h1>
        <p>Customer ID: {{customer_id}}</p>
        <p>Date: {{generation_date}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Borrower Information</h2>
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{customer_name}}</p>
        <p><strong>Customer ID:</strong> {{customer_id}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Loan Details</h2>
        <div class="loan-details">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Loan Amount:</td>
                    <td>{{loan_amount}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Interest Rate:</td>
                    <td>{{interest_rate}} per annum</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Term:</td>
                    <td>{{term_months}} months</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Loan Type:</td>
                    <td>Bitcoin-backed loan</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>
        <p>1. <strong>Repayment:</strong> The borrower agrees to repay the loan amount plus interest according to the agreed schedule.</p>
        
        <p>2. <strong>Collateral:</strong> This loan is secured by Bitcoin collateral held by Lana Bank.</p>
        
        <p>3. <strong>Default:</strong> In case of default, Lana Bank reserves the right to liquidate the collateral to recover the outstanding amount.</p>
        
        <p>4. <strong>Interest:</strong> Interest will be calculated and charged according to the agreed rate and schedule.</p>
        
        <p>5. <strong>Governing Law:</strong> This agreement is governed by applicable banking regulations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-box">
            <p>Borrower Signature</p>
            <p>{{customer_name}}</p>
            <p>Date: _____________</p>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-box">
            <p>Lana Bank Representative</p>
            <p>Name: _____________</p>
            <p>Date: _____________</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; text-align: center;">
        <p>This document was generated electronically by Lana Bank on {{generation_date}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>